{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22717ee35d","title":"对新华社关于内地对香港副食品供应量锐减的报道的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7ec97c0558","index":0,"year":1959,"month":1,"day":25,"articleId":"22717ee35d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"d453147da7","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"},{"id":"7efa5a9878","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"新华通讯社1959年1月22日编印的《内部参考》第二六九一期上登载的该社香港分社记者组写的这一报道说，香港副食品绝大部分历来是依靠内地供应的。最近一个月来，内地对香港供应量锐减，在各阶层人士中引起了很大波动。在广大的中间、落后居民中，流露着一种热惧、仿律和不满情绪，糊涂看法很多；在进步人士中，认识还算比较清楚，但也有各种疑虑；反动派目前也在利用这个机会大肆进行反动宣传。"},{"id":"adec51ab5a","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时正在北京召开的各省、市、自治区党委书记会议。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2749773b0f","type":"title","text":"对新华社关于内地对香港副食品供应量锐减的报道的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d"},{"id":"d453147da7","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d"},{"id":"7efa5a9878","type":"paragraph","text":"此件有用，请印发到会同志们一读。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d"},{"id":"adec51ab5a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d"},{"id":"13bfb90a63","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d"}],"page":{"id":"5d988f5f53","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"22717ee35d","start":182,"end"